name: Gold's Gym: Cardio Workout
overview: Gold's Gym: Cardio Workout brings your own personal Gold's Gym cardio trainer into your living room! Gold's Gym is the largest gym in the world and is known for leading the industry in personal training, so expect to get in shape fast. It's a fun way to exercise and maintain a healthy body.
